Name:           geary
Version:        43.0
Release:        0
Summary:        An email reader for the GNOME desktop
License:        BSD-2-Clause AND CC-BY-3.0 AND LGPL-2.1-or-later
Group:          Productivity/Networking/Email/Clients
URL:            https://wiki.gnome.org/Apps/Geary
